Question No.: 185

Title: Department Top Three Salaries

Difficulty: Hard

Language: MySQL

Use DENSE_RANK() to rank unique salaries within each department, then keep only the top 3 ranks.

SELECT
    d.name AS Department,
    e.name AS Employee,
    e.salary AS Salary
FROM (
    SELECT
        name,
        salary,
        departmentId,
        DENSE_RANK() OVER (
            PARTITION BY departmentId
            ORDER BY salary DESC
        ) AS salary_rank
    FROM Employee
) e
JOIN Department d
ON e.departmentId = d.id
WHERE e.salary_rank <= 3;

